# PATHFIND::IS_NAVMESH_REQUIRED_REGION_IN_USE

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether a script is using the navmesh region (including the calling script)
